<p class="bibl">Griffin, Randall C. <span class="book">Homer, Eakins and Anshutz: The Search for American Identity in the Gilded Age … Winslow Homer, Avatar of Americanness</span>. Pennsylvania: Pennsylvania University Press, 2004.
